Graduation_Project/
│── esp32_simulation/       # ESP32 Sensor Data Simulation
│   ├── esp32_simulator.py  # Generates fake sensor readings & sends data
│   ├── thingspeak_sender.py  # Sends data to ThingSpeak
│
│── backend/  
│       ├── templates/
│   │       ├── index.html      # Web UI for monitoring              # Flask Backend API
│   ├── server.py           # Main API handling sensor data
│   ├── database.py         # SQLite database setup
│   ├── requirements.txt    # Dependencies
│
│── frontend/               # Web Dashboard (HTML, JS)

│   ├── static/
│   │   ├── styles.css      # Frontend styling (optional)
│   ├── app.py              # Flask app to serve the web dashboard
│
│── README.md               # Project Documentation
│── .gitignore              # Ignore unnecessary files
│── requirements.txt        # Install all dependencies